        </tabular>
    </table>

    <p>This next table illustrates these prefixes in the context of length (meters). Notice how it is easier to avoid the fractions (last three entries).</p>

    <table xml:id="table-metric-metric-conversion">
        <title>Metric Conversion</title>
        <tabular top="medium">
            <row bottom="medium" left="medium"><cell right="medium">Scaled Unit</cell><cell right="medium">Base Unit</cell></row>
            <row bottom="medium" left="medium"><cell right="medium">kilometer (km)</cell><cell right="medium"><m>10^3=1000</m> meters</cell></row>
